ot \"Oracle Code Assist\"","author_association":"NONE","pin":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anomalyco/opencode/issues/comments/4246010164/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"minimized":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anomalyco/opencode/issues/comments/4468492916","html_url":"https://github.com/anomalyco/opencode/issues/20465#issuecomment-4468492916","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anomalyco/opencode/issues/20465","id":4468492916,"node_id":"IC_kwDOOiiGL88AAAABClfKdA","user":{"login":"kkugot","id":5512139,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjU1MTIxMzk=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5512139?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/kkugot","html_url":"https://github.com/kkugot","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kkugot/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kkugot/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kkugot/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kkugot/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kkugot/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kkugot/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kkugot/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kkugot/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kkugot/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2026-05-16T23:11:51Z","updated_at":"2026-05-16T23:11:51Z","body":"To the OCA users of opencode:\nI found an OCA upstream Responses streaming issue while debugging OpenCode visibility failures. For some /v1/responses stream=true post-tool requests, upstream returns HTTP 200 but then closes the SSE stream with no useful output, sometimes only lifecycle events or even bytes:0. This happens intermittently across endpoints, so it does not look like a single bad endpoint or issue with opencode. The workaround in this PR was forcing opencode to do a retry. I added OCA proxy-side protection to hide those broken attempts from the client and retry before committing downstream SSE, which resolved the OpenCode rendering issue in my local testing. We need to bring this issue to OCA team now.","author_association":"NONE","pin":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anomalyco/opencode/issues/comments/4468492916/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"minimized":null}]